:: A Doorway on Dean Street {"position":"700,550","size":"100,100"}
(set: $hadBreather to true)\
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 12)
A doorway. Set back from the street, out of the sodium light. The stone is cool against your back.

(if: $hadPhoneCall is true)[You close your eyes and see them: Aoife in the dark flat, the baby wrapped in whatever she could find. You can't stop now.]

[[Continue|Dean Street]]

