[[Serve|PP Pong]]

:: Chinese Fish and Chips {"position":"100,1300","size":"100,100"}
<div class="chippy-scene">
<div class="chippy-light top"></div>
<div class="chippy-light bottom"></div>
<svg class="chippy-tube" viewBox="0 0 300 18" width="100%" height="18" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><filter id="fgA" x="-20%" y="-120%" width="140%" height="400%"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/><feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge></filter></defs><!-- Cold blue outer glow --><rect x="14" y="1" width="272" height="16" rx="6" fill="rgba(180,210,255,0.22)" filter="url(#fgA)"/><!-- Tube body — harsh cold white with blue tint --><rect x="16" y="4" width="268" height="10" rx="4" fill="rgba(215,230,255,0.96)"/><!-- Bright core stripe --><rect x="18" y="6" width="264" height="4" rx="2" fill="rgba(240,248,255,1.0)"/><!-- End caps — grey metal --><rect x="12"  y="3" width="7" height="12" rx="2" fill="rgba(130,135,145,0.75)"/><rect x="281" y="3" width="7" height="12" rx="2" fill="rgba(130,135,145,0.75)"/><!-- Faint internal line suggesting the fluorescent tube --><line x1="22" y1="9" x2="278" y2="9" stroke="rgba(200,220,255,0.4)" stroke-width="0.7"/></svg>
(set: $hadChippy to true)\
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 15)\
(set: $sobriety to $sobriety + 20)
You find it down a side street, where you always knew it was but had forgotten: the Chinese Fish and Chips.

The fluorescent light inside is a brutality after all that amber and shadow. A woman behind the counter doesn't look up. The radio plays something you almost recognise.

You order cod and chips. The vinegar is sharp and the grease is holy. You eat standing at the narrow counter, watching the night drift past the steamed-up window.

|lily1>[<div class="lily-prompt" style="display:inline-block; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:50%; width:2.5em; height:2.5em; line-height:2.5em; text-align:center; cursor:pointer;">⚘</div>]\
(click-replace: ?lily1)[(set: $lilyCount to $lilyCount + 1)<span class="lily-glimpse lily-fade">That must be her, as tall as the Amazon; her joints articulate how you remember.</span>]

For a few minutes, you are nobody. You have no manuscript. You owe nothing to anyone.

The warmth spreads through you. The fog lifts, just a little.

[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]
