(if: $sobriety > 100)[(set: $sobriety to 100)]
(if: $sobriety < 0)[(set: $sobriety to 0)]
(if: $sobriety <= 0 and $haunts's length >= 3)[(goto: "Coach and Horses lock")](else-if: $sobriety <= 0)[(set: $sobriety to 5)//You stagger. Nearly fell. Catch yourself on a lamppost. The street blurs then steadies. You need to keep it together.//]
(if: $confidence <= 5 and not (($alba contains $alba1) and ($alba contains $alba2) and ($alba contains $alba3)))[[[Give up on the book|No more]]]
(else-if: $confidence <= 25)[<span class="greyed-out">//The street feels longer than it did an hour ago.//</span>]
(if: $wasBeaten is true and $visitedInterval is true)[<span class="fetch-glimpse">You see him then: yourself, walking ahead of you down Greek Street toward Centre Point. He does not look back. He walks the way a man walks when he has made a decision. You know where he is going. You have always known.</span>]
}
<span class="scene-date">(if: $afterMidnight)[24.11.73](else:)[23.11.73]</span>
<span class="scene-location">Dean Street, Soho, London.</span>

A heavy afternoon lingers in rainfall on the pavements though the sky has cleared now and the newborn night is cut with moonshine.

There is an atmosphere of the silver screen: as if Brando might emerge in a tight and sodden T-shirt, from any door or alleyway, anytime.

(if: $returns >= 7 and $afterMidnight is false)[(set: $afterMidnight to true)](if: $returns >= 7)[The small hours creep. Windows darken overhead. Even Dean Street must eventually sleep.
](else-if: $returns >= 5)[It's deep into the night now. The puddles have dried to dark stains on the stone.
](else-if: $returns >= 3)[The evening wears on. Fewer faces in the street. The ones still out have reasons to be.
](if: $lilyCount >= 4)[<span class="lily-thought">She is very close now, too close. So close that you see yourself only through her eyes, which once walked next to you; whose viewpoint is more distant than expected; from where you seem to be walking utterly alone.</span>
](else-if: $lilyCount >= 2)[<span class="lily-thought">Lily-of-the-Valley — her scent, its refined toxicity — found you twice now. Perhaps you need to trail it, dog that you are.</span>
](if: $lilyCount > 0)[(display: "Lily SVG")]\
In your bag, you have your novel in manuscript. You need to sell it, pronto.

(if: $haunts's length >= 5)[Something shifts again. Eyes meet you and doors open like they used to. Keep on.
](else-if: $haunts's length >= 3)[Something shifts. The faces start to know your face again. A girl at the French waves through the reeded glass. It's beginning to let you in.
](if: $hadPhoneCall is true)[Aoife's voice echoes: //Try harder.// The baby. The cold flat. No milk. No heat. No time.
](if: $metRed is true)[Where do you go?
(if: $visited's French is not true or $exploredSinceFrench is true)[[[To The French|Approach The French]]
](else:)[<span class="greyed-out">The French — you can hear the murmur through the reeded glass</span>
]\
(if: $visited's French is true)[[[To The Pillars of Hercules|Maritime interlude]]
]\
(if: $visited's French is true)[[[Try the Colony Room|Approach The Colony Room]]
]\
(if: $knowsRonnies is true and $completedSetlist is false)[[[Hear the jazz at Ronnie Scott's|Ronnie Scott's]]
](else-if: $knowsRonnies is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Ronnie Scott's — the set drifts out, muffled, into the street</span>
]\
(if: $knowsLackland is true and $knowsCopperSecret is true)[[[Go to Lackland's Office|Approach Lacklands Office]]
](else-if: $knowsLackland is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Lackland's Office — the light is on, but you need the password</span>
]\
(if: $knowsCecilCourt is true and $returnedPage is false)[[[Visit the antiquarian in Cecil Court|Cecil Court]]
](else-if: $returnedPage is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Cecil Court — the shop is dark now</span>
]\
(if: $hasTrishaMatchbook is true and not ($haunts contains $haunt8))[[[Try Trisha's|Failure: Trisha's]]
](else-if: $haunts contains $haunt8)[<span class="greyed-out">Trisha's — a taxi idles outside, someone leaving</span>
]\
(if: ($alba contains $alba1) and ($alba contains $alba2) and not ($alba contains $alba3))[[[The voice|Late Lily]]
]]
(else:)[Who's that on the corner?

[[See who's there|Approach The Ginger Light]]]
(if: $confidence < 40 and $hadBreather is false)[You're feeling worn down. There's a quiet doorway nearby.

[[Step into the doorway|A Doorway on Dean Street]]
](else-if: $hadBreather is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Step into the doorway</span>
]\
(if: $confidence < 50 and $sobriety < 50 and $hadChippy is false)[You're in a bad way. But there's a place you know, down a side street. The Chinese Fish and Chips.

[[Get something to eat|Chinese Fish and Chips]]
](else-if: $hadChippy is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Get something to eat</span>
]\
(set: $notebookUnlocked to true)\
(if: ($alba contains $alba1) and ($alba contains $alba2) and ($alba contains $alba3))[[[Go to Dawn|Dawn]]]

