:: Escape success {"position":"2200,1350","size":"100,100"}
You bolt for the stairs. Copper shouts something but you're already gone, back through the Colony Room door and onto Dean Street.

Your hands are shaking. Your jaw hurts. But you're still standing.

[[Dean Street|Dean Street]]

:: Failure: Trisha's {"position":"700,1400","size":"100,100"}
(if: $hasTrishaMatchbook is true)[The bouncer looks you up and down. He's about to turn you away when you remember the matchbook.

You hold it up. He takes it, turns it over, examines the worn edges.

'Harsent,' he says. Not a question.

He steps aside.

[[Enter Trisha's|Trisha's]]]
(else:)[(set: $confidence to $confidence - 18)

They do not know you.

[[Dean Street|Dean Street]]]

:: Fight Defeat [venue-cellar] {"position":"2000,1350","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Swinging bulb -->
<div class="cellar-bulb-wrap">
<svg width="48" height="90" viewBox="0 0 48 90"><line x1="24" y1="0" x2="24" y2="30" stroke="#888878" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.75"/><rect x="17" y="28" width="14" height="10" rx="2.5"fill="rgba(80,78,65,0.9)" stroke="rgba(160,155,120,0.7)" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="19" y="36" width="10" height="3" rx="1"fill="none" stroke="rgba(150,145,110,0.55)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="60" rx="20" ry="22"fill="rgba(255,245,160,0.12)"/><path d="M24,38 C16,38 10,45 10,55 C10,67 16,78 24,78 C32,78 38,67 38,55 C38,45 32,38 24,38 Z"fill="rgba(255,252,210,0.95)" stroke="rgba(220,210,160,0.6)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="57" rx="9" ry="11"fill="rgba(255,240,120,0.55)"/><path d="M18,60 L20,53 L24,58 L28,53 L30,60"fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,200,40,0.95)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/><rect x="20" y="75" width="8" height="3" rx="1"fill="rgba(200,195,155,0.65)" stroke="none"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-lose">🥊 DOWN 🥊</span></div>
</div>

You are on the floor. The cellar ceiling rotates slowly above you, like a thought you cannot complete. Copper stands over you, barely winded; he could do this all night and you both know it.

'Brave,' he says. 'Stupid, but brave.'

[[Try to get up|Beaten]]

:: Fight R1 Back {"position":"2100,750","size":"100,100"}
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-lose">CAUGHT</span></div>
</div>

You step back but the wall has other ideas; it meets you like an old debt. Copper's fist finds your shoulder and spins you like a thought he's having about you.

'No room down here,' he says. 'Did nobody mention?'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]

:: Fight R1 Block {"position":"2000,750","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)\
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">ABSORBED</div>
</div>

You get your arms up. The impact travels through your bones like news through a small town: everyone knows at once.

You are still standing. This surprises you both.

'You can take one,' says Copper. 'Good. There's more where that came from.'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]

:: Fight R1 Duck {"position":"1900,750","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 2)\
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">CLEAN</span></div>
</div>

You fold beneath it. His knuckles whistle through the space where your skull had been, where it is not, where it will never be again.

For a breath he is off-balance; in his eyes you see a question form.

'Quick,' he admits. 'Let's see about lucky.'

[[Round 2|Fight Round 2]]

:: Fight R2 Catch {"position":"2000,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)\
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">ABSORBED</div>
</div>

You catch his wrist. For a moment you are locked together, breathing each other's air, intimate as lovers or as enemies; in Soho these are often the same.

He wrenches free. The jab dies undelivered.

'Interesting,' he says. 'Most writers don't fight back.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]

:: Fight R2 Counter {"position":"2100,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: _counterChance to (random: 1, 10))
(if: _counterChance >= 6)[(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 3)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">★ COUNTER ★</span></div>
</div>

You let the jab come. It rocks your head back; stars bloom behind your eyes like flowers in a cemetery. But your own fist is already travelling, and it finds the soft country beneath his ribs.

Copper folds. The sound he makes is not language.

'Bastard,' he gasps, when he can. But his eyes are smiling.

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]]
(else:)[<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-lose">CAUGHT</span></div>
</div>

You try to counter but your body is slower than your ambition. His jab snaps your head back. Blood in your mouth, copper-bright. The cellar swims like something seen through bathwater.

'Don't get clever,' says Copper. 'Clever gets you dead.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]]

:: Fight R2 Slip {"position":"1900,950","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 2)\
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">CLEAN</span></div>
</div>

You slip sideways; his knuckles graze your cheek like a rumour, like something that nearly happened but didn't.

He grunts. Annoyance or respect; the Maltese don't differentiate.

'Slippery,' he says. 'Like a poet.'

[[Round 3|Fight Round 3]]

:: Fight R3 Clinch {"position":"2000,1150","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 1)\
You step inside his reach and clinch him. His uppercut has nowhere to go; it dies against your shoulder. You are chest to chest now, breathing hard, close as dancers, close as grief.

(if: $fightScore >= 4)[[[Push him off|Fight Victory]]]
(else:)[[[He throws you|Fight Defeat]]]

:: Fight R3 Headon {"position":"2100,1150","size":"100,100"}
(set: _finalChance to (random: 1, 10))
(if: _finalChance >= 5)[(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 3)

You charge. His uppercut glances off your shoulder like a confession off a priest. Your forehead meets his nose; there is a sound like a book closing.

[[He staggers|Fight Victory]]]
(else:)[His uppercut finds you clean. The ceiling and the floor exchange positions; you are no longer certain which is which.

[[Darkness|Fight Defeat]]]

:: Fight R3 Weave {"position":"1900,1150","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to $fightScore + 2)\
You weave. The uppercut passes through the space you have just vacated, like a train through an empty station. Copper stumbles forward, momentum betraying him.

(if: $fightScore >= 4)[[[The opening|Fight Victory]]]
(else:)[[[He recovers|Fight Defeat]]]

:: Fight Round 1 {"position":"2000,650","size":"100,100"}
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">🥊 ROUND 1 🥊</div>
</div>

Copper feints left. You clock it; he clocks you clocking it. Then the right hook comes, wide as a sermon, and the air ahead of his fist arrives first like a herald.

[[Duck under it|Fight R1 Duck]]
[[Block with your forearms|Fight R1 Block]]
[[Step back|Fight R1 Back]]

:: Fight Round 2 {"position":"2000,850","size":"100,100"}
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">🥊 ROUND 2 🥊</div>
</div>

Copper circles. He has the patience of geography; he could do this until the mountains erode. Then he drives forward—a jab, straight as a sermon, aimed at the bridge of your nose.

[[Slip to the side|Fight R2 Slip]]
[[Catch his wrist|Fight R2 Catch]]
[[Take it and counter|Fight R2 Counter]]

:: Fight Round 3 {"position":"2000,1050","size":"100,100"}
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">🥊 ROUND 3 🥊</div>
</div>

The final exchange. Copper breathes harder now; so do you. The cellar air is thick with what you've both been spending.

He feints twice—left, left—then throws everything he has into an uppercut that starts somewhere near his knees.

[[Weave away|Fight R3 Weave]]
[[Clinch him|Fight R3 Clinch]]
[[Meet him head-on|Fight R3 Headon]]

:: Fight Victory [venue-cellar] {"position":"2000,1250","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Swinging bulb -->
<div class="cellar-bulb-wrap">
<svg width="48" height="90" viewBox="0 0 48 90"><line x1="24" y1="0" x2="24" y2="30" stroke="#888878" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.75"/><rect x="17" y="28" width="14" height="10" rx="2.5"fill="rgba(80,78,65,0.9)" stroke="rgba(160,155,120,0.7)" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="19" y="36" width="10" height="3" rx="1"fill="none" stroke="rgba(150,145,110,0.55)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="60" rx="20" ry="22"fill="rgba(255,245,160,0.12)"/><path d="M24,38 C16,38 10,45 10,55 C10,67 16,78 24,78 C32,78 38,67 38,55 C38,45 32,38 24,38 Z"fill="rgba(255,252,210,0.95)" stroke="rgba(220,210,160,0.6)" stroke-width="0.8"/><ellipse cx="24" cy="57" rx="9" ry="11"fill="rgba(255,240,120,0.55)"/><path d="M18,60 L20,53 L24,58 L28,53 L30,60"fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,200,40,0.95)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/><rect x="20" y="75" width="8" height="3" rx="1"fill="rgba(200,195,155,0.65)" stroke="none"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">🥊 STANDING 🥊</span></div>
</div>

Copper kneels. Blood on his lip like punctuation. He looks up at you and you see something in his face that might be respect, or might be the thing that comes before respect in men like him.

'Alright,' he says. 'Alright.'

Quiet Frankie has not moved; Quiet Frankie may never move again. Ashton Granger scribbles like her life depends on it. Perhaps it does.

'You've got stones,' says Copper, rising. 'Wrong door, but stones.'

He jerks his thumb toward the stairs: the universal gesture for //go, before I change my mind//.

'Tell whoever sent you that Salvu Copper doesn't forget a face.'
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 8)
[[Escape up the stairs|Escape success]]

:: Fight starts [venue-cellar] {"position":"2000,550","size":"100,100"}
(set: $fightScore to 0)\
<span id="sob-data" style="display:none;">(print: $sobriety)</span>
<div id="pre-fight">
<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score">🥊 THE CELLAR 🥊</div>
