The cellar contracts like a lung. Copper rolls his shoulders; the sound of them is tectonic.

Quiet Frankie looks up for the first time. Even the shadows lean in.

'Three goes,' says Copper. 'More than most get.'

He raises his fists in the old style, the Queensberry style, the style of men who learned violence before it had rules.

