(if: $opponent is "Harsent")[Harsent laughs. Hands you a folded paper.

'A line. Can't find its poem. Maybe you can.']
(else:)[Clegg hands you a slip of paper.

'From an old pamphlet. Seventeenth century. Take it.']

You unfold the paper:

<div class="revelation-box">
<em>"Between the acting of a dreadful thing / And the first motion, all the interim is / Like a phantasma, or a hideous dream."</em>
</div>

It's not the Alba. But it's something.

