<div class="ronnies-scene">
<div class="ronnies-spot"></div>
<div class="ronnies-cone"></div>
<svg class="ronnies-rule" viewBox="0 0 300 20" width="100%" height="20" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="rnG" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#6888b8" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="22%"  stop-color="#8aacdc" stop-opacity="0.75"/><stop offset="50%"  stop-color="#aac8f0" stop-opacity="0.90"/><stop offset="78%"  stop-color="#8aacdc" stop-opacity="0.75"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#6888b8" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="rnGd" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#405880" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="25%"  stop-color="#6070a0" stop-opacity="0.45"/><stop offset="75%"  stop-color="#6070a0" stop-opacity="0.45"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#405880" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><radialGradient id="rnSpill" cx="50%" cy="100%" r="60%"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#e8c060" stop-opacity="0.18"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e8c060" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><rect x="30" y="0" width="240" height="22" fill="url(#rnSpill)"/><line x1="0" y1="18" x2="300" y2="18" stroke="url(#rnGd)" stroke-width="0.7"/><line x1="0" y1="22" x2="300" y2="22" stroke="url(#rnG)"  stroke-width="2.2"/><line x1="0" y1="25" x2="300" y2="25" stroke="url(#rnGd)" stroke-width="0.8"/><polygon points="150,19 153,22 150,25 147,22" fill="#aac8f0" opacity="0.7"/><circle cx="100" cy="22" r="1.2" fill="#8aacdc" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="200" cy="22" r="1.2" fill="#8aacdc" opacity="0.5"/></svg>

From jazz you can learn more about prose than you can about poetry.

The last note hangs itself from the rafters. The room's dead still.

Moe nods. 'Go sell a book,' he says.

