(set: $sobriety to $sobriety - 18)\
(set: $exploredSinceFrench to true)\
(unless: $visited is a datamap)[(set: $visited to (dm:))]\
(unless: $visited contains "Ronnies")[(set: $visited's Ronnies to false)]\
(if: $visited's Ronnies is not true)[(set: $visited's Ronnies to true)\
<div class="first-visit-hint">RONNIE SCOTT'S. THE MUSICIANS MIGHT NEED DRINKS.</div>]

The stairs down to Ronnie Scott's smell of smoke and possibility; the bass notes find you before the light does, a pulse in the brickwork, a heartbeat in the walls.

Inside, the room is smaller than legend suggests. The ceiling presses down, thick with decades of exhalation. On stage, two musicians rest between sets like boxers between rounds.

|lily3>[<div class="lily-prompt" style="display:inline-block; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:50%; width:2.5em; height:2.5em; line-height:2.5em; text-align:center; cursor:pointer;">⚘</div>]\
(click-replace: ?lily3)[(set: $lilyCount to $lilyCount + 1)<span class="lily-glimpse lily-fade">You've the sense, distinct as cordial, that Lily is sitting behind you but looking risks too much.</span>]

The trumpeter: a thin man with sad eyes and immaculate cuffs, polishing his horn with a cloth like a man polishing a memory. Beside him, the bassist—bald head like Stravinsky, painted nails, kingly swagger—tunes and retunes a string that is already perfect. They call him Jazz Cousin.

They clock you watching. The trumpeter nods.

'You look lost,' he says. 'Lost people buy drinks.'

Moe de Alcousin smiles; his teeth are piano keys. 'He means: fetch us something from the bar. We're parched as Lent.'

(if: $completedSetlist is not true)[[[What are you having?|RS Drink Orders]]
[[Just here to listen|RS Just Listen]]]
(else:)[<div class="venue-exhausted">They've played out all they have to play, there's no more here tonight.</div>

[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]]
<svg class="ronnies-rule" viewBox="0 0 300 14" width="100%" height="14" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="rnG2" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#6888b8" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="22%"  stop-color="#8aacdc" stop-opacity="0.75"/><stop offset="50%"  stop-color="#aac8f0" stop-opacity="0.90"/><stop offset="78%"  stop-color="#8aacdc" stop-opacity="0.75"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#6888b8" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="rnGd2" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%"   stop-color="#405880" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="25%"  stop-color="#6070a0" stop-opacity="0.45"/><stop offset="75%"  stop-color="#6070a0" stop-opacity="0.45"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#405880" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient></defs><line x1="0" y1="4"  x2="300" y2="4"  stroke="url(#rnGd2)" stroke-width="0.7"/><line x1="0" y1="7"  x2="300" y2="7"  stroke="url(#rnG2)"  stroke-width="2.2"/><line x1="0" y1="10" x2="300" y2="10" stroke="url(#rnGd2)" stroke-width="0.8"/><polygon points="150,4 153,7 150,10 147,7" fill="#aac8f0" opacity="0.7"/><circle cx="100" cy="7" r="1.2" fill="#8aacdc" opacity="0.5"/><circle cx="200" cy="7" r="1.2" fill="#8aacdc" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
</div>

