<svg class="carthage-coast" viewBox="0 0 500 60" width="100%" height="60" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><linearGradient id="ccSky" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1a1a3a" stop-opacity="0.6"/><stop offset="60%" stop-color="#c89050" stop-opacity="0.25"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d4a060" stop-opacity="0.1"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="ccSea" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2a5080" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1a3050" stop-opacity="0.3"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="ccSand" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#c8a870" stop-opacity="0.4"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#a08050" stop-opacity="0.2"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="ccFade" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="1"/><stop offset="8%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="92%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0a12" stop-opacity="1"/></linearGradient></defs><rect x="0" y="0" width="500" height="32" fill="url(#ccSky)"/><ellipse cx="250" cy="32" rx="200" ry="8" fill="#d4a060" opacity="0.15"/><rect x="0" y="28" width="500" height="14" fill="url(#ccSea)"/><path d="M0,32 Q30,30 60,33 T120,32 T180,33 T240,31 T300,33 T360,32 T420,33 T500,32" fill="none" stroke="#5a8ab8" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.45"/><path d="M0,35 Q25,33 50,36 T100,34 T150,36 T200,34 T250,36 T300,34 T350,36 T400,34 T450,36 T500,35" fill="none" stroke="#4a7aa8" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.3"/><rect x="0" y="40" width="500" height="20" fill="url(#ccSand)"/><path d="M0,42 Q40,40 80,42 T160,41 T240,42 T320,40 T400,42 T500,41" fill="none" stroke="#c8a870" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="62" y="10" width="5" height="32" fill="#a09878" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="60" y="8" width="9" height="3" rx="0.5" fill="#b0a888" opacity="0.55"/><rect x="52" y="38" width="8" height="4" rx="1" fill="#a09878" opacity="0.35" transform="rotate(-12,56,40)"/><line x1="63" y1="12" x2="63" y2="40" stroke="#8a8268" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.4"/><line x1="66" y1="12" x2="66" y2="40" stroke="#8a8268" stroke-width="0.4" opacity="0.4"/><rect x="425" y="4" width="6" height="38" fill="#a09878" opacity="0.45"/><rect x="422" y="2" width="12" height="3" rx="0.5" fill="#b0a888" opacity="0.5"/><path d="M427,15 L429,20 L427,25" fill="none" stroke="#706850" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="436" y="36" width="10" height="5" rx="1" fill="#a09878" opacity="0.3" transform="rotate(8,441,38)"/><rect x="238" y="18" width="3" height="14" fill="#706880" opacity="0.25"/><rect x="248" y="20" width="3" height="12" fill="#706880" opacity="0.2"/><path d="M236,18 L254,18" fill="none" stroke="#706880" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.18"/><circle cx="80" cy="6" r="0.6" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="180" cy="4" r="0.5" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.35"/><circle cx="320" cy="7" r="0.7" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="410" cy="3" r="0.5" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="150" cy="10" r="0.4" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.25"/><circle cx="370" cy="9" r="0.4" fill="#c8c8e0" opacity="0.25"/><rect x="0" y="0" width="500" height="60" fill="url(#ccFade)"/></svg>

You bottled it but you've found safe harbour in Carthage, which is not like you remember it at all. These days it is swamped with Romans.

The last time you were here, you recall only Scipio Aemilianus, who was weeping and who said:

<div class="verse">
'A day will come when Ilium shall perish,<br>
And Priam and his people shall be slain.'
</div>

You think about that still, sometimes, in England.

You see two paths:

On the hill a woman burns upon a pyre.

And past the beach, a little bar: The Green Sea.

[[Approach the pyre|Dido]]
(if: $haunts's length >= 3)[[[Go to The Green Sea|LINE 2]]](else:)[//The Green Sea feels distant.//]
[[Wake from this dream|Dream to Dean]]

:: Dream to Dean {"position":"300,1550","size":"100,100"}
The columns dissolve. Salt air becomes petrol and rain.

You blink. You're standing on Dean Street again, shivering, unsure how long you were gone. The pavement is wet and real beneath your feet.

[[Continue|Dean Street]]

:: The critic's judgement {"position":"300,1400","size":"100,100"}
