:: You speak to the poet {"position":"1400,450","size":"100,100"}
(set: $metRed to true)\
<!-- Ginger light -->
<div class="ginger-lamp-wrap">
<svg width="60" height="110" viewBox="0 0 60 110"><ellipse cx="30" cy="33" rx="40" ry="30" fill="rgba(200,100,5,0.10)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="31" rx="24" ry="18" fill="rgba(220,130,10,0.18)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="29" rx="13" ry="10" fill="rgba(255,190,60,0.22)"/><polygon points="27,2 30,0 33,2 32,7 28,7" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><path d="M13,7 Q30,4 47,7 L44,13 L16,13 Z" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><path d="M16,13 L44,13 L40,44 L20,44 Z" fill="rgba(130,75,8,0.45)" stroke="rgba(90,52,4,0.65)" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M19,15 L41,15 L37,42 L23,42 Z" fill="rgba(255,165,35,0.42)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="29" rx="7" ry="10" fill="rgba(255,232,130,0.55)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="27" rx="3" ry="4" fill="rgba(255,250,210,0.68)"/><rect x="22" y="44" width="16" height="6" rx="2.5" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><rect x="27" y="50" width="6" height="60" rx="2" fill="rgba(45,28,3,0.90)"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="ginger-scene">
<div class="ginger-light"></div>
'Red!' you say. He looks up at first, then towards you without looking at you.

'I need to sell a book.'

'Sell yourself,' he says. 'Things turn up.'

You understand.

As you turn, you strike, in the cool and marbling air, a vein of his perfume, which you recognise, because you once loved a woman who wore that scent, as lily-of-the-valley.

<span class="lily-thought">And with it, her risen face:

//That is not natural in an age like this,
Being high and solitary and most stern//</span>
<span class="lily-thought">A little earthquake in the heart upsets the world and you are twenty-one again, walking with her on your arm through the rain on St. Giles, past the funfair, before so very much went so far wrong.</span>(set: $confidence to $confidence - 12)

[[Walk on|LINE 1]]
</div>

