::In Copper&#39;s lair [venue-cellar] {"position":"1600,700"}
'Come in then,' says Copper.

You do as you're told as he closes the door behind you.

'Downstairs,' says Copper.

You don't remember it being downstairs.

Salvu Copper is a big man in a small body, or perhaps it's the other way round, you can't be sure.

You barrel yourself into a cellar, cold and pale. It extends to your left, beneath the colony rooms and probably one plot further.

You turn to Copper, who has just joined you from the stairs.

[[Turn to Copper|Turn to Copper]]

::Jeffrey Bernard&#39;s Cow {"position":"700,1200"}
'Will you do something about this cow?'

Said Jeffrey Bernard.

You take its bridle. It sneezes. When you look back he's disappeared to a timeshare on the seacoast of Bohemia.

