::Shana&#39;s Verdict [venue-trishas] {"position":"900,1850"}
'Nothing,' she says. 'That's the thing. Nothing is wrong with it. It's just nothing.'

She pushes it back towards you. You return it to your bag like something injured.

'I love you but you need to get to work. Bring it to me six months down the line.'
